{"id":443,"category_slug":"english-conversations","category_name":"Conversations","position":45,"title":"45. A Cup of Coffee","subtitle":"","level":"A2","parts":14,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/english-conversations/45-a-cup-of-coffee.443/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/45-a-cup-of-coffee-2022-03-07-21-20-04/0-45-a-cup-of-coffee.mp3","transcript":"Can I get you something to drink?\nA cup of coffee, please.\nWith milk and sugar?\nA little milk, but no sugar.\nI never drink coffee at night.\nWhy not?\nIt keeps me awake.\nWhat do you drink with supper?\nTea, it helps me relax.\nI don't like tea.\nThere are so many kinds of tea;\nmaybe you should shop around and try to find one you like\nbecause coffee is bad for you.\nThat's a good idea.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T20:48:45","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Can I get you something to drink?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/45-a-cup-of-coffee-2022-03-07-21-20-04/1.mp3","time_start":2.97,"time_end":4.44},{"position":2,"content":"A cup of coffee, please.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/45-a-cup-of-coffee-2022-03-07-21-20-04/2.mp3","time_start":4.44,"time_end":5.8},{"position":3,"content":"With milk and sugar?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/45-a-cup-of-coffee-2022-03-07-21-20-04/3.mp3","time_start":5.8,"time_end":7.15},{"position":4,"content":"A little milk, but no sugar.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/45-a-cup-of-coffee-2022-03-07-21-20-04/4.mp3","time_start":7.15,"time_end":8.76},{"position":5,"content":"I never drink coffee at night.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/45-a-cup-of-coffee-2022-03-07-21-20-04/5.mp3","time_start":8.76,"time_end":10.62},{"position":6,"content":"Why not?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/45-a-cup-of-coffee-2022-03-07-21-20-04/6.mp3","time_start":10.62,"time_end":11.32},{"position":7,"content":"It keeps me awake.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/45-a-cup-of-coffee-2022-03-07-21-20-04/7.mp3","time_start":11.27,"time_end":12.58},{"position":8,"content":"What do you drink with supper?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/45-a-cup-of-coffee-2022-03-07-21-20-04/8.mp3","time_start":12.93,"time_end":14.29},{"position":9,"content":"Tea, it helps me relax.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/45-a-cup-of-coffee-2022-03-07-21-20-04/9.mp3","time_start":14.37,"time_end":16.68},{"position":10,"content":"I don't like tea.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/45-a-cup-of-coffee-2022-03-07-21-20-04/10.mp3","time_start":16.68,"time_end":17.74},{"position":11,"content":"There are so many kinds of tea;","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/45-a-cup-of-coffee-2022-03-07-21-20-04/11.mp3","time_start":17.78,"time_end":19.7},{"position":12,"content":"maybe you should shop around and try to find one you like","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/45-a-cup-of-coffee-2022-03-07-21-20-04/12.mp3","time_start":19.74,"time_end":23.5},{"position":13,"content":"because coffee is bad for you.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/45-a-cup-of-coffee-2022-03-07-21-20-04/13.mp3","time_start":23.5,"time_end":25.56},{"position":14,"content":"That's a good idea.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/45-a-cup-of-coffee-2022-03-07-21-20-04/14.mp3","time_start":25.63,"time_end":26.93}]}